{"thig6.3:0.1":"Therigatha 6.3 ","thig6.3:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thig6.3:0.3":"Khematherigatha ","thig6.3:1.1":"“Dahara tvam rupavati, ","thig6.3:1.2":"ahampi daharo yuva; ","thig6.3:1.3":"Pancangikena turiyena, ","thig6.3:1.4":"ehi kheme ramamase”. ","thig6.3:2.1":"“Imina putikayena, ","thig6.3:2.2":"aturena pabhanguna; ","thig6.3:2.3":"Attiyami harayami, ","thig6.3:2.4":"kamatanha samuhata. ","thig6.3:3.1":"Sattisulupama kama, ","thig6.3:3.2":"khandhasam adhikuttana; ","thig6.3:3.3":"Yam ‘tvam kamaratim’ brusi, ","thig6.3:3.4":"‘arati’ dani sa mama. ","thig6.3:4.1":"Sabbattha vihata nandi, ","thig6.3:4.2":"tamokhandho padalito; ","thig6.3:4.3":"Evam janahi papima, ","thig6.3:4.4":"nihato tvamasi antaka. ","thig6.3:5.1":"Nakkhattani namassanta, ","thig6.3:5.2":"aggim paricaram vane; ","thig6.3:5.3":"Yathabhuccamajananta, ","thig6.3:5.4":"bala suddhimamannatha. ","thig6.3:6.1":"Ahanca kho namassanti, ","thig6.3:6.2":"sambuddham purisuttamam; ","thig6.3:6.3":"Pamutta sabbadukkhehi, ","thig6.3:6.4":"satthusasanakarika”ti. ","thig6.3:7.1":"… Khema theri …. "}